snippet.title: Call of Duty Modern Warfare 2 and Warzone - Official Seaon 6 BlackCell Trailer (ft. Spawn)
snippet.description: Players can now upgrade their Battle Pass in Season 6 to the BlackCell for Call of Duty Modern Warfare 2 and Warzone. Earn new skins and content now with the BlackCell Upgrade for Call of Duty Modern Warfare 2 and Warzone launching on September 27.
